    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? This car is an absolute gem and has been pampered since day one! It\u2019s in flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it. You won't find a cleaner one out there, so come take a look before it's gone!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
