    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear, and the carpets are immaculate. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the smallest switch, functions with factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history and exclusively original parts. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a virtually new example of this model. Inspections are welcomed to verify its flawless state.",
      "price": 43500.0,
